  <summary>2/13/2001--Introduced.
Lower Regulatory Burden for Homeowners Act of 2001 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to include customer connection fees (including fees to connect a customer's line to or extend a main water or sewer line) as an excludable corporate income item within the definition of "contribution in aid of construction."</summary>
